= author;\n        }\n    }\n\n    @Entity(\"reference_mapper_authors\")\n    public static final class Author {\n        @Id\n        private String id;\n\n        private Author() {\n        }\n\n        private Author(final String id) {\n            this.id = id;\n        }\n    }\n}\n"}}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 1783, "output": 961, "cacheRead": 40960, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 43704, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "toolUse", "timestamp": 1782707205569, "responseId": "resp_0c6da4d601b12865016a41f40607dc8190b4cecc2f055d5fe2"}, "toolResults": [{"role": "toolResult", "toolCallId": "call_MtDi39SdtrU7aQK6MERX6pKV|fc_0c6da4d601b12865016a41f40ef3388190aa8958be8aca8cd0", "toolName": "write", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Successfully wrote 1798 bytes to tests/src/org.mongodb.morphia/morphia/1.3.2/src/test/java/org_mongodb_morphia/morphia/ReferenceMapperTest.java"}], "isError": false, "timestamp": 1782707217884}]}
